overview.zh: 胤福通证RBCC是以通证经济为基础打造的实业智慧城市生态系统，是区块链+城市开发+银行金融的大应用融合体系，利用系统的全产业区块链技术，全球各种行业应用均可加入RBCC智慧生态系统，实现各行各业的全面落地应用。
overview.en: RBCC is an industrial smart city ecosystem based on the CIS economy, which is a large application integration system of block-chain + urban development + banking finance. By utilizing the system's whole industry block-chain technology, the RBCC Smart Ecosystem can be applied to various industries worldwide, which realizes comprehensive applications of all walks of life.
